codex
The vault confirms a useful detail: `deposit()` mints against `calcPoolValueInToken()` across all lenders, and `rebalance()` is public and calls `_withdrawAll()`. That means a stale Compound position can still matter even if `provider` is Aave or something else, as long as the vault still holds any cUSDT.
