codex
I found the concrete root cause of the current failure from the trace, and it’s not the economic logic. The PoC hardcodes `0x39AA...` as “cUSDT”, but the live vault’s Compound market at this fork is the address returned by `vault.compound()`; the trace shows it is `0xf650...`, so the PoC was measuring the wrong cToken and bailing out on a false `NoCompoundPosition`.
